@startuml
title TruNotesv2 - Critical Path Method (CPM) Diagram
top to bottom direction

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor White
    BorderColor Black
    ArrowColor Black
}

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor<<Critical>> #FFCCCC
    BorderColor<<Critical>> Red
    FontColor<<Critical>> Red
    BorderThickness<<Critical>> 2
}

skinparam arrow {
    Color<<Critical>> Red
    Thickness<<Critical>> 2
}

' Define Tasks
component "A: Start & Setup\n(2 Days)" as A <<Critical>>
component "B: Auth System\n(4 Days)" as B
component "C: Local DB Setup\n(3 Days)" as C <<Critical>>
component "D: Global Design\n(5 Days)" as D
component "E: AI Bridge Imp.\n(6 Days)" as E
component "F: Editor Engine\n(8 Days)" as F <<Critical>>
component "G: Notes UI & CRUD\n(10 Days)" as G <<Critical>>
component "H: Sync Engine\n(6 Days)" as H <<Critical>>
component "I: AI Features\n(5 Days)" as I
component "J: Tasks & Calendar\n(4 Days)" as J
component "K: Refining & Polish\n(6 Days)" as K <<Critical>>
component "L: Release\n(1 Day)" as L <<Critical>>

' Define Dependencies based on analysis
A -down-> B
A -down-> C <<Critical>>
A -down-> D

C -down-> E
C -down-> F <<Critical>>

F -down-> G <<Critical>>

B -down-> H
G -down-> H <<Critical>>
G -down-> J

E -down-> I

' Convergence to K
D -down-> K
H -down-> K <<Critical>>
I -down-> K
J -down-> K

K -down-> L <<Critical>>

note right of L
  **Total Duration:** 36 Days
  **Critical Path:** Red Nodes
end note

@enduml
